Detailed Description

HSI Data Card Header.

The HSI Data Card Header is used by the TI Data card while configured to operate in Multi-Mode

uint16_t HSIDataCardHeader_t::totalLengthMSW

Total length (in BYTES) of all the data which is being streamed. This is the higher 12 bits. Application developers can use the helper function to get the total length of the packet. The size excludes the data card header.
